Summary: Regulator to dig deeper into links between banks and other firms. EBA chief says it will do more to regulate crypto: FT The EBA will work with regulators to understand the impact of a shadow banking system. A report by the EU's financial stability watchdog says the banking system is resilient.

The emergence of a bullish pattern on Chainlink’s price chart added to an optimistic outlook. Chainlink is currently trading above $15, data from Coingecko shows. Chainlink shows signs of a bull pennant formation. A decisive close above $17.2 could be the catalyst Chainlink is in a bullish position and that there is a possibility of a break. Technical analysis plays an important role in trading decisions.

Ethereum to be Van de Poppe’s top crypto pick this year. He also suggests that Bitcoin could rally to $20,000 Ethereum’s deflationary nature, brought about by its switch to a proof-of-stake consensus Layer-2 scaling solution, Optimism, is printing a bullish pattern. Chainlink is on trader’s list of crypto ‘top four’. .
